0: SELECT MAX(s.FreeMealCountK12) / s.EnrollmentK12 FROM schools s WHERE s.County = 'Alameda'	----- bird -----	california_schools
1: SELECT `Free Meal Count (Ages 5-17)` / `Enrollment (Ages 5-17)` FROM `schools` WHERE `School Type` = 'Continuation Schools' ORDER BY `Free Meal Count (Ages 5-17)` / `Enrollment (Ages 5-17)` ASC NULLS LAST LIMIT 3;	----- bird -----	california_schools
2: SELECT Zip FROM frpm WHERE Charter School (Y/N) = 1	----- bird -----	california_schools
3: SELECT `Street` FROM `schools` WHERE `CDSCode` = (SELECT `CDSCode` FROM `frpm` ORDER BY `FRPM Count (K-12)` DESC LIMIT 1)	----- bird -----	california_schools
4: SELECT `Phone` FROM frpm INNER JOIN satscores ON frpm.CDSCode = satscores.CDSCode WHERE frpm.Enrollment (Ages 5-17) > 0 AND frpm.Charter School (Y/N) = 1	----- bird -----	california_schools
5: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T1.CDSCode) FROM schools AS T1 JOIN inspections AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode JOIN violations AS T3 ON T1.CDSCode = T3.CDSCode WHERE T2.AvgScrMath > 400 AND T3.rtype = 'F'	----- bird -----	california_schools
6: SELECT DISTINCT T1.School FROM schools AS T1 JOIN satscores AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T2.NumTstTakr > 500 AND T1.Magnet = 1	----- bird -----	california_schools
7: SELECT `Phone` FROM `schools` WHERE `CDSCode` = (SELECT `CDSCode` FROM `satscores` WHERE `NumTstTakr` = (SELECT MAX(`NumTstTakr`) FROM `satscores` WHERE `AvgScrMath` > 1500))	----- bird -----	california_schools
8: SELECT COUNT(T1.enroll12) FROM schools AS T1 JOIN satscores AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T2.FRPM Count (K-12) = (SELECT MAX(T2.FRPM Count (K-12)) FROM schools AS T3 JOIN satscores AS T4 ON T3.CDSCode = T4.CDSCode)	----- bird -----	california_schools
9: SELECT COUNT(T1.CDSCode) FROM satscores AS T1 JOIN frpm AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T1.AvgScrMath > 560 AND T2.Charter Funding Type = 'Directly funded'	----- bird -----	california_schools
10: SELECT T1.FRPM_Count_Ages_5_17 FROM schools AS T1 JOIN satscores AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T2.AvgScrRead IS NOT NULL ORDER BY T2.AvgScrRead DESC LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
11: SELECT DISTINCT T1.CDSCode FROM schools AS T1 JOIN frpm AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T1.Enrollment(K-12) + T1.Enrollment(Ages 5-17) > 500	----- bird -----	california_schools
12: SELECT MAX(T1.eligible_free_rate) FROM satscores AS T1 INNER JOIN schools AS T2 ON T1.cds = T2.CDSCode WHERE T1.SAT_excellence_rate > 0.3	----- bird -----	california_schools

17: SELECT T1.CDSCode, T1.Percent_Percent_Eligible_Free_Ages_5_17, T1.Percent_Percent_Eligible_FRPM_Ages_5_17, T1.Percent_Percent_Eligible_Free_Ages_5_17 AS FreeMealCount, T1.Percent_Percent_Eligible_FRPM_Ages_5_17 AS EligibleFree, T1.Percent_Percent_Eligible_FRPM_Ages_5_17 AS EligibleFRPM FROM schools AS T1 JOIN satscores AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.cds WHERE T2.AvgScrWrite > 499 ORDER BY T2.AvgScrWrite DESC	----- bird -----	california_schools

19: SELECT T1.Phone FROM schools AS T1 JOIN satscores AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.cds WHERE T2.AvgScrMath = (SELECT MAX(AvgScrMath) FROM satscores) ORDER BY T1.Phone ASC LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools

27: SELECT s.School, AVG(f.AvgScrWrite) AS AvgScoreInWriting, COALESCE(s.Phone, 'No Phone Number') AS CommunicationNumber FROM schools s JOIN frpm f ON s.CDSCode = f.CDSCode WHERE (s.OpenDate > '1991-12-31' OR s.ClosedDate < '2000-12-31') GROUP BY s.School, s.Phone ORDER BY AvgScoreInWriting DESC	----- bird -----	california_schools
28: SELECT s1.Name, s1.DOCType FROM schools s1 JOIN frpm f1 ON s1.CDSCode = f1.CDSCode JOIN schools s2 ON f1.School Code = s2.School Code WHERE f1.Enrollment (K-12) - f1.Enrollment (Ages 5-17) > (SELECT AVG(s2.Enrollment (K-12) - s2.Enrollment (Ages 5-17)) FROM schools s2)	----- bird -----	california_schools

35: SELECT `AdmEmail1` FROM `frpm` WHERE `Charter School (Y/N)` = 1 ORDER BY `Enrollment (K-12)` ASC NULLS LAST LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
36: SELECT AdmFName1, AdmFName2, AdmLName1, AdmLName2 FROM schools WHERE NumGE1500 = ( SELECT MAX(NumGE1500) FROM schools ) ORDER BY AdmFName1, AdmFName2, AdmLName1, AdmLName2 LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
37: SELECT T1.Street, T1.City, T1.State, T1.Zip FROM schools AS T1 JOIN satscores AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T2.ExcellenceRate = (SELECT MIN(NumGE1500 / NumTstTakr) FROM satscores) ORDER BY T1.Zip ASC LIMIT 1	----- bird -----	california_schools
38: SELECT `satscores`.`cds`, `schools`.`Website` FROM `satscores` AS `T1` INNER JOIN `schools` AS `T2` ON `T1`.`cds` = `T2`.`CDSCode` WHERE `T1`.`NumTstTakr` BETWEEN 2000 AND 3000	----- bird -----	california_schools
39: SELECT AVG(enroll12) FROM schools WHERE OpenDate BETWEEN '1980-01-01' AND '1980-12-31'	----- bird -----	california_schools
40: SELECT `Phone` FROM `schools` WHERE `cds` IN (SELECT `cds` FROM `satscores` WHERE `dname` = 'Fresno Unified' ORDER BY `AvgScrRead` ASC LIMIT 1)	----- bird -----	california_schools
41: SELECT T1.School FROM schools AS T1 JOIN satscores AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.cds WHERE T1.Virtual = 'F' ORDER BY T2.AvgScrRead DESC LIMIT 5;	----- bird -----	california_schools
42: SELECT EdOpsName FROM schools WHERE AvgScrMath = (SELECT MAX(AvgScrMath) FROM satscores)	----- bird -----	california_schools
43: SELECT AVG(s.AvgScrMath) AS avg_math_score, s.County FROM schools s JOIN satscores a ON s.CDSCode = a.cds GROUP BY s.County ORDER BY AVG(s.AvgScrMath) ASC LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
44: SELECT satscores.cname AS school_name, satscores.city AS city_name, AVG(satscores.AvgScrWrite) AS avg_writing_score FROM satscores JOIN schools ON satscores.CDSCode = schools.CDSCode WHERE satscores.NumGE1500 > 0 GROUP BY satscores.cname, satscores.city ORDER BY AVG(satscores.AvgScrWrite) DESC LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
45: SELECT s1.cname, AVG(s1.AvgScrWrite) FROM schools s1 JOIN satscores s2 ON s1.cds = s2.cds JOIN schools s3 ON s1.cds = s3.cds WHERE s3.AdmFName1 = 'Ricci' AND s3.AdmFName2 = 'Ulrich' GROUP BY s1.cname	----- bird -----	california_schools
46: SELECT DISTINCT T1.School FROM schools AS T1 JOIN frpm AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T1.DOCType = 'State Special Schools' AND T1.Grades BETWEEN 'K' AND '12' ORDER BY T2.Enrollment DESC LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	california_schools
47: SELECT AVG(T1.`FRPM Count (Ages 5-17)`) AS MonthlyAverage FROM schools AS T1 JOIN frpm AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T1.DOC = '52' AND T1.Year = 1980 GROUP BY T1.Year	----- bird -----	california_schools

957: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT driverId) FROM drivers WHERE time IS NULL AND nationality = 'Italian'	----- bird -----	formula_1
958: SELECT DISTINCT T1.forename, T1.surname FROM drivers AS T1 JOIN results AS T2 ON T1.driverId = T2.driverId WHERE T2.fastestLapTime = (SELECT MIN(fastestLapTime) FROM results)	----- bird -----	formula_1
959: SELECT fastestLap FROM results WHERE year = 2009 AND statusId = (SELECT statusId FROM status WHERE status = 'D') ORDER BY time ASC LIMIT 1	----- bird -----	formula_1
960: SELECT AVG(T1.fastestLapSpeed) FROM races AS T1 JOIN results AS T2 ON T1.raceId = T2.raceId WHERE T1.name = 'Spanish Grand Prix' AND T1.year = 2009	----- bird -----	formula_1
961: SELECT r.name AS race_name, r.year AS race_year FROM races r JOIN results rs ON r.raceId = rs.raceId WHERE rs.milliseconds IS NOT NULL ORDER BY rs.milliseconds ASC LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	formula_1
962: SELECT CAST(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN T1.year(dob) < 1985 AND T1.laps > 50 THEN T1.driverId ELSE NULL END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(DISTINCT T2.driverId) FROM drivers AS T1 JOIN races AS T2 ON T1.driverId = T2.driverId WHERE T1.year(dob) < 1985 AND T1.laps > 50	----- bird -----	formula_1
963: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T1.driverId) FROM drivers AS T1 JOIN lapTimes AS T2 ON T1.driverId = T2.driverId WHERE T2.seconds < 120 AND T1.nationality = 'French'	----- bird -----	formula_1
964: SELECT T1.code FROM drivers AS T1 JOIN constructors AS T2 ON T1.driverId = T2.constructorId WHERE T2.nationality = 'America'	----- bird -----	formula_1
965: SELECT raceId FROM races WHERE year = 2009;	----- bird -----	formula_1
966: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT driverId)  FROM results  WHERE raceId = 18;	----- bird -----	formula_1
967: SELECT COUNT(T1.id) FROM pitStops AS T1 INNER JOIN constructors AS T2 ON T1.constructorId = T2.constructorId WHERE T1.constructorId IN (SELECT T3.constructorId FROM constructors AS T3 WHERE T3.name = 'Netherlands') AND T1.year BETWEEN 1900 AND 1992	----- bird -----	formula_1
968: SELECT T1.driverRef FROM drivers AS T1 INNER JOIN results AS T2 ON T1.driverId = T2.driverId WHERE T2.driverId = (SELECT driverId FROM drivers WHERE surname = 'Kubica' AND forename = 'Robert')	----- bird -----	formula_1
969: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T1.driverId) FROM drivers AS T1 JOIN constructors AS T2 ON T1.constructorId = T2.constructorId JOIN constructorStandings AS T3 ON T2.constructorId = T3.constructorId WHERE T1.nationality = 'British' AND T1.dob = '1980-01-01'	----- bird -----	formula_1

1031: SELECT T1.player_api_id, T1.player_name, T1.height, T1.birthday, T1.weight, T1.sprint_speed, T1.age FROM Player AS T1 JOIN (     SELECT player_api_id, player_name, height, birthday, weight, sprint_speed, age     FROM Player     WHERE sprint_speed >= 97     AND YEAR(date) >= 2013     AND YEAR(date) <= 2015 ) AS T2 ON T1.player_api_id = T2.player_api_id WHERE T1.age > 0 ORDER BY T1.age DESC	----- bird -----	european_football_2
1032: SELECT L.name, COUNT(T.league_id) AS match_count FROM League AS L JOIN Match AS T ON L.id = T.league_id GROUP BY L.id ORDER BY match_count DESC LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	european_football_2
1033: SELECT AVG(T1.height)  FROM Player AS T1  WHERE T1.birthday >= '1990-01-01 00:00:00' AND T1.birthday < '1996-01-01 00:00:00';	----- bird -----	european_football_2
1034: SELECT T1.player_api_id FROM Player AS T1 JOIN Player_Attributes AS T2 ON T1.player_api_id = T2.player_api_id WHERE T2.overall_rating = (SELECT MAX(T2.overall_rating) FROM Player AS T3 JOIN Player_Attributes AS T4 ON T3.player_api_id = T4.player_api_id WHERE T3.date LIKE '2010-%') AND T2.date LIKE '2010-%';	----- bird -----	european_football_2
1035: SELECT T1.team_fifa_api_id FROM Team AS T1 JOIN Team_Attributes AS T2 ON T1.team_api_id = T2.team_api_id WHERE T2.buildUpPlaySpeed > 50 AND T2.buildUpPlaySpeed < 60	----- bird -----	european_football_2
1036: SELECT T1.team_long_name FROM Team AS T1 JOIN Team_Attributes AS T2 ON T1.team_api_id = T2.team_api_id WHERE T2.buildUpPlayPassing > (SUM(T2.buildUpPlayPassing) / COUNT(T1.team_long_name)) AND strftime('%Y', T1.date) = '2012' GROUP BY T1.team_long_name HAVING COUNT(T1.team_long_name) > 1	----- bird -----	european_football_2
